NOTICE
======

This file lists every third-party crate `hsh` redistributes in its
compiled binaries, grouped by license. Generated from the workspace
`Cargo.lock` by `cargo about generate`.

The licenses that appear here are limited to the accept-list in
`about.toml`. Run `make sbom` to regenerate after a dep change.

{{#each licenses as |license|}}
## {{license.name}} ({{license.id}})

The following crates are licensed under {{license.id}}:

{{#each license.used_by}}
- **{{this.crate.name}} {{this.crate.version}}** — {{#if this.crate.description}}{{this.crate.description}}{{/if}}
{{/each}}

### License text

```
{{license.text}}
```

{{/each}}
